title: Man vs Child Chef Showdown S01E01 HDTV.x264-POKE.mp4
description:
In each episode of Man vs Child: Chef Showdown, a team of five child cooking prodigies will challenge a prolific executive-level chef in the kitchen, where they will defend their culinary abilities. Will raw talent and imagination prove to be enough for the first generation of kids raised on cooking shows? Great chefs will be put to the ultimate test, against the food stars of tomorrow.




Man vs. Child: Chef Showdown - Season 1, Episode 1


Don't Under-ESTIE-Mate Her

Executive Chef Frank Otte tests his mettle against a team of five child cooking prodigies; from "finger foods" to a "technique trio," can this acclaimed executive chef hold his own against 7-year old child chef Estie? Master Chef Suzanne Tracht joins to blind taste and judge the winner takes all final round.


Original Air Date: 23-Jul-2015
